{"hb3cfbe27g1ad1g42beg889eg8a791d2be44a": ["You should leave. Auntie isn't receiving guests just now.", "74dcb337-e6d1-4329-ac2b-5a3723346159", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_Hag_MaskedVictim4.html", "ee6e3a9b-93c4-8fe8-28fc-ff431beedc69"], "hd8264e40gb7ebg4c8cgb009g1ca42d8152d9": ["Quiet, please. Auntie is resting.", "74dcb337-e6d1-4329-ac2b-5a3723346159", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_Hag_MaskedVictim4.html", "393430b6-248a-def6-993e-dffbe2dbc886"], "h2b6ae855g8627g408eg9a75ge5d1cc410e36": ["'Auntie' is dead - I killed her.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_Hag_MaskedVictim4.html", "69212bfd-58b4-b072-220c-46fd28046041"], "h2dba96fag9f8dg4bebg992dgb2ade5822599": ["Very droll, sir. Most amusing.", "74dcb337-e6d1-4329-ac2b-5a3723346159", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_Hag_MaskedVictim4.html", "0bddef56-88d0-9856-0aaf-5536b98a4b7f"], "h24d07e6cg8185g4cc3ga9c5g43e7d5a9121e": ["Very droll, madam. Most amusing.", "74dcb337-e6d1-4329-ac2b-5a3723346159", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_Hag_MaskedVictim4.html", "0bddef56-88d0-9856-0aaf-5536b98a4b7f"], "hb3a3ceb7g0f30g44d5g9abcgc6b4edaf8550": ["Auntie cannot die.", "74dcb337-e6d1-4329-ac2b-5a3723346159", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_Hag_MaskedVictim4.html", "deae3930-fd15-5674-ab03-a40d62625caa"], "hddb29731g2a69g4107g97beg4443d15322a7": ["Sleeping. Of course - everything's fine.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_Hag_MaskedVictim4.html", "3c8681b2-64f2-7caa-ebb1-679fc847be2e"], "hfbb5fc9egff75g483dgb61egcf11895208e6": ["Oh dear - I forget to plump her pillows this morning!", "74dcb337-e6d1-4329-ac2b-5a3723346159", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_Hag_MaskedVictim4.html", "c7ad69b9-e281-b040-47d4-6e226b95400f"], "h6e642ebeg57d6g43ccga9f9g6e0dcb81611b": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_Hag_MaskedVictim4.html", "ae766eb0-49fb-3940-4b96-90fd2f965f2e"], "h14ac67f6ge6ccg4f6fgb33eg4470e8606e45": ["Did something happen to auntie? I can't feel her anymore.", "74dcb337-e6d1-4329-ac2b-5a3723346159", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_Hag_MaskedVictim4.html", "afb786f8-e60f-5f1f-9ca6-324fb5d5a725"], "h2fe60a0bg0021g4d8ag8d71g4854dc64d47e": ["Are you here to see Auntie? Sorry the place is such a mess.", "74dcb337-e6d1-4329-ac2b-5a3723346159", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_Hag_MaskedVictim4.html", "b1a3b3d9-e7cb-f720-7c92-aaac6cb9877a"]}